### Get All Demands (Paged)
GET {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/demands?pageIndex=1&pageSize=5&status=active
Accept: application/json

### Get Demand by ID
GET {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/demands/1
Accept: application/json

### Get Demands by Category
GET {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/demands/category/1
Accept: application/json

### Create Demand (Admin)
POST {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/demands
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "categoryId": 1,
  "name": "Gaming",
  "status": "active"
}

### Update Demand (Admin)
PUT {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/demands/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "categoryId": 1,
  "name": "Heavy Gaming",
  "status": "active"
}

### Delete Demand (Admin)
DELETE {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/demands/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
